be.ac.ua.ansymo.cheopsj.model
Class ModelManager

java.lang.Object
  be.ac.ua.ansymo.cheopsj.model.ModelManager
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class ModelManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

This class is the entity that holds and maintains the entire famix and change model. All famixEntities and all changes that act upon those famixEntities are stored in this ModelManager.

Author:
quinten

getInstance

public static ModelManager getInstance()
The ModelManger is a Singleton entity. Therefor the constructor is private. This method returns an instance of the ModelManger. If no instance existed before it will call the private constructor to create a new instance. Else It will return the existing instance.
